 has an amber colour and a whitish head. A bouquet of orange blossom and a sweet touch of honey. It has a creamy carbon flavour and has just the right amount of acidity."},{"id":"fr_FR","ocurrence":0,"type":"STRING","value":"Gènesis Toronja mêle tradition et avant-garde. Le classicisme vient de son élaboration artisanale (sans conservateurs ni colorants), la nouveauté de l'ajout de fleurs d'oranger."},{"id":"fr_FR","ocurrence":1,"type":"STRING","value":"Mélange parfait d'eau, de malt, de houblon, de riz et de fleur d'oranger. Elle présente une couleur ambrée et sa mousse délicate est blanchâtre. Au nez on retrouve l'élégance de la fleur d'oranger et une touche sucrée de miel. En bouche les bulles sont crémeuses et l'acidité idéale."}]}]},{"id":"GestionComprasStock","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"Calificacion1","type":"STRING","value":"A"},{"id":"Calificacion2","type":"STRING","value":"A"},{"id":"Calificacion4","type":"STRING","value":"2A"},{"id":"Calificacion5","type":"STRING","value":"ME"},{"id":"TipoDeGestion","type":"STRING","value":"16"}]},{"id":"DimensionesYPeso","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"UOM!Dimensiones!Unidad","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"204","id_Ext":"347186090","value":"cm"},{"id":"UOM!PesoBruto!Unidad","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"206","id_Ext":"347187090","value":"g"},{"id":"UOM!VolumenContenidoNeto!VolumenContenidoNeto","type":"NUMBER","value":"0.0"},{"id":"UOM!VolumenContenidoNeto!Unidad","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"213","id_Ext":"347188090","value":"ml"},{"id":"PUM","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"EnlacePUM","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"2530","id_Ext":"20552573090","value":"005"},{"id":"CantidadProducto","type":"NUMBER","value":"33.0"},{"id":"UnidadesProducto","type":"STRING","value":"001"}]}]},{"id":"ColoresYTallas","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"ColorFabricante","type":"STRING","value":"MEDITERRANEA"},{"id":"TamanoHorma","type":"STRING","value":"AZAHAR Y ARROZ"},{"id":"Dibujo",